IS HOW TO RESOLVE CONFLICTS
AMONG THEMSELVES.

00:12:37.660 --> 00:12:41.460
AND BASICALLY, YOU CAN LOOK
AT HUMAN MORALITY AS A SYSTEM

00:12:41.460 --> 00:12:43.960
THAT RESOLVES CONFLICTS
AMONG PARTIES

00:12:43.960 --> 00:12:45.660
THAT LIVE IN ONE SOCIETY.

00:12:45.660 --> 00:12:48.400
DOES THAT LEAD YOU TO THINK
IN A DIFFERENT WAY

00:12:48.400 --> 00:12:51.730
ABOUT THE ORIGINS OF HUMAN
MORALITY THAN YOU DID BEFORE?

