HUMAN MORALITY MUST HAVE
SOME DEEP EVOLUTIONARY ROOTS.

00:12:55.100 --> 00:12:56.830
IT MUST COME FROM SOMEWHERE

00:12:56.830 --> 00:13:00.860
AND PROBABLY IN OTHER ANIMALS,
WE CAN FIND NOT THE WHOLE SYSTEM

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:04.000
BUT WE CAN FIND CERTAIN ELEMENTS
OF HUMAN MORALITY

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:07.800
AND THAT'S WHAT I'M SEEING
WHEN I LOOK AT CHIMPANZEES.

00:13:09.300 --> 00:13:12.560
Alda:
CHIMPANZEES ARE OUR CLOSEST
NONHUMAN RELATIVES.

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:16.060
BUT THEY'RE NOT THE ONLY
PRIMATES WITH A CODE OF ETHICS.

00:13:16.060 --> 00:13:19.600
EVEN THOUGH THEY BRANCHED OFF
FROM US 40 MILLION YEARS AGO

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:23.230
THERE'S A SPECIES OF MONKEY
THAT ALSO TRADES TIT FOR TAT--

00:13:23.230 --> 00:13:24.730
CAPUCHINS.

00:13:26.730 --> 00:13:28.600
CAPUCHINS ARE BEING STUDIED

00:13:28.600 --> 00:13:32.330
BY ONE OF FRANS DE WAAL'S
RESEARCH STUDENTS, LISA PARR.

00:13:32.330 --> 00:13:34.060
CAPUCHINS ARE
WELL KNOWN

00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:37.030
FOR BEING VERY
MANIPULATIVE IN THEIR FOOD.

00:13:37.030 --> 00:13:39.560
SO YOU CAN SEE
THAT THEY'LL... OOPS.

00:13:39.560 --> 00:13:42.400
HE WASN'T TOO GOOD
ABOUT THAT MANIPULATION.

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:45.560
HE WANTS THE WHOLE BUNCH,
NOT JUST A PIECE.

00:13:45.560 --> 00:13:47.400
THEY ALSO HAVE
LARGE BRAINS

00:13:47.400 --> 00:13:48.830
FOR THEIR BODY SIZE.

00:13:48.830 --> 00:13:52.060
IT'S THE LARGEST AMONG
THE NEW WORLD MONKEYS.

00:13:52.060 --> 00:13:54.230
AND THEY ALL HAVE
CREWCUTS, TOO.

00:13:56.230 --> 00:14:00.460
TODAY'S EXPERIMENT WILL INVOLVE
"BIAS," A FEMALE CAPUCHIN...

00:14:00.460 --> 00:14:03.130
Woman:
COME ON, VINCENT.

00:14:03.130 --> 00:14:05.800
Alda:
AND VINCENT, A MALE COLLEAGUE.

00:14:12.300 --> 00:14:15.160
VINCENT IS GIVEN
A BUCKET OF APPLES.

00:14:15.160 --> 00:14:18.730
THEN IT'S TIME FOR US
TO DISCREETLY WITHDRAW.

00:14:23.760 --> 00:14:26.300
THESE TWO ARE
VERY TOLERANT
OF ONE ANOTHER.

00:14:26.300 --> 00:14:28.100
THEY'RE SITTING
CLOSE TOGETHER

00:14:28.100 --> 00:14:31.400
DOING WHAT WE'VE TERMED
"PASSIVE FOOD SHARING."

00:14:31.400 --> 00:14:32.900
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

00:14:32.900 --> 00:14:35.030
IT MEANS THAT
THE FOOD POSSESSOR

00:14:35.030 --> 00:14:36.560
IS SITTING
CLOSE ENOUGH

00:14:36.560 --> 00:14:38.130
SO THAT
DISCARDED PIECES

00:14:38.130 --> 00:14:39.800
AND BROKEN
BITS OF PIECES

00:14:39.800 --> 00:14:42.860
ARE WITHIN REACH OF THE
PASSIVE FOOD PARTNER.

00:14:42.860 --> 00:14:44.600
BECAUSE HE'S NOT
PREVENTING HER

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:46.730
FROM TAKING THE FOOD,
THAT'S SHARING.

00:14:46.730 --> 00:14:48.330
IS THERE
ANY INDICATION

00:14:48.330 --> 00:14:51.060
HE'S LEAVING THESE
PIECES DELIBERATELY

00:14:51.060 --> 00:14:52.330
IN SOME WAY?

00:14:52.330 --> 00:14:54.400
I MEAN, IS HE
JUST A SLOPPY EATER

00:14:54.400 --> 00:14:56.730
THAT DOESN'T CARE
WHO GRABS HIS FOOD?

00:14:56.730 --> 00:14:59.300
WELL, WE HAVE CONTROL
STUDIES THAT WE DO

00:14:59.300 --> 00:15:02.030
WHERE THERE'S ONLY
ONE ANIMAL IN THE CAGE

00:15:02.030 --> 00:15:03.900
AND UNDER THOSE
CIRCUMSTANCES

00:15:03.900 --> 00:15:06.860
THE ANIMAL USUALLY DOESN'T
SIT CLOSE TO THE MESH

00:15:06.860 --> 00:15:09.300
SO THE PIECES AREN'T
LEFT WITHIN REACH.

00:15:09.300 --> 00:15:13.230
Alda:
SO CAPUCHINS, TOO,
SHARE AND SHARE ALIKE.

00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:18.700
IT SEEMS THAT NO MATTER WHAT
PRIMATE SPECIES HE LOOKS AT

00:15:18.700 --> 00:15:22.730
FRANS DE WAAL FINDS EVIDENCE
OF COOPERATION AND PEACEMAKING.

00:15:22.730 --> 00:15:25.300
Alda:
IT SEEMS KIND OF
A REASSURING IDEA

00:15:25.300 --> 00:15:34.230
THAT THIS DRIVE FOR HOLDING DOWN
VIOLENCE COMES NATURALLY TO...

00:15:34.230 --> 00:15:39.030
TO OUR COUSINS
AND PROBABLY TO US.

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:40.830
I'M GLAD YOU SAID "NATURALLY"

00:15:40.830 --> 00:15:43.230
BECAUSE USUALLY PEOPLE
USE ANIMALS ONLY

00:15:43.230 --> 00:15:45.230
FOR THE BAD SIDE
OF HUMAN NATURE.

00:15:45.230 --> 00:15:47.060
LIKE WHAT PEOPLE DO IN RWANDA

00:15:47.060 --> 00:15:49.260
WE SAY THEY ARE
ACTING LIKE ANIMALS.

00:15:49.260 --> 00:15:52.560
AS SOON AS WE DO SOMETHING BAD
IT'S BEASTLY BEHAVIOR.

00:15:52.560 --> 00:15:53.960
IF WE DO SOMETHING GOOD

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:56.500
IT'S OUR NOBLE HUMAN NATURE
THAT CAUSES IT

00:15:56.500 --> 00:15:58.660
AND I THINK WE HAVE
BOTH SIDES IN US

00:15:58.660 --> 00:16:01.430
AND WE CAN SEE BOTH SIDES
IN OTHER PRIMATES

00:16:01.430 --> 00:16:05.130
IS THAT WE HAVE AGGRESSIVE
TENDENCIES, VIOLENT TENDENCIES.

00:16:05.130 --> 00:16:06.660
BUT AT THE SAME TIME

00:16:06.660 --> 00:16:10.130
WE HAVE MECHANISMS TO DEAL
WITH THESE ISSUES.

00:16:23.060 --> 00:16:25.000
Alda:
LIKE HUMAN BABIES

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:28.160
CHIMP BABIES ARE DEPENDENT
ON THEIR MOTHERS

00:16:28.160 --> 00:16:31.430
WHEN THEY'RE BORN AND
FOR A LONG TIME AFTERWARDS

00:16:31.430 --> 00:16:33.860
AS THEY LEARN TO
BECOME GOOD CHIMPS.

00:16:33.860 --> 00:16:36.000
BUT WHEN CHIMPS ARE
BORN IN CAPTIVITY

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:38.630
MOTHERS DON'T SEEM ABLE
TO TEACH THEIR BABIES

00:16:38.630 --> 00:16:40.560
THE PROPER RULES
OF CHIMP SOCIETY.

00:16:40.560 --> 00:16:44.360
SO AT YERKES, BABIES ARE BROUGHT
HERE TO THE CHIMP NURSERY

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:48.860
WHERE IT'S UP TO HUMANS TO TEACH
THEM HOW TO BECOME GOOD CHIMPS.

00:16:48.860 --> 00:16:50.260
ABANDONED AT BIRTH

00:16:50.260 --> 00:16:53.860
THREE-WEEK-OLD JULIE IS
NOW BEING RAISED BY KIM BARD

00:16:53.860 --> 00:16:56.630
WHO TRIES TO BE
AS CHIMPLIKE AS SHE CAN.

00:16:56.630 --> 00:16:58.760
Bard:
WE NURTURE THEM AS BABIES

00:16:58.760 --> 00:17:00.100
CHIMPANZEE-STYLE.

00:17:00.100 --> 00:17:02.400
WE DON'T WANT THEM TO BE HUMANS

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:04.930
WE WANT THEM TO BE
GOOD CHIMPANZEES.

00:17:04.930 --> 00:17:07.930
SO HUMAN BABIES
YOU WOULD FEED LYING DOWN

00:17:07.930 --> 00:17:09.960
CHIMP BABIES EAT LIKE THIS.

