IS THAT A SMILE?

00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:17.400
YES, THAT'S
A SMILE.

00:17:17.400 --> 00:17:19.700
SHE SMILES WITH
THE BOTTOM TEETH

00:17:19.700 --> 00:17:21.400
A LITTLE
LIKE BOB HOPE.

00:17:21.400 --> 00:17:23.600
THEY SMILE WITH
THE BOTTOM GUMS

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:25.130
IN HER CASE, SHOWING.

00:17:25.130 --> 00:17:26.900
IF YOU SEE
THE TOP TEETH

00:17:26.900 --> 00:17:29.830
IT'S BY DEFINITION NOT
A SMILE ON A CHIMPANZEE.

00:17:29.830 --> 00:17:34.060
Alda:
LIKE HUMAN BABIES, CHIMP BABIES
ARE MAGNETS TO ADULTS.

00:17:34.060 --> 00:17:36.960
I MUST BE AT LEAST
AS PROGRAMMED AS SHE IS

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:39.330
BECAUSE I GOT A LOT
MORE INTERESTED

00:17:39.330 --> 00:17:41.660
AS SOON AS SHE
GRABBED MY FINGERS.

00:17:41.660 --> 00:17:45.500
DO YOU FIND
THAT HAPPENING
IN A MOTHER CHIMP

00:17:45.500 --> 00:17:47.900
IF THE BABY GRABS
ONTO HER?

00:17:47.900 --> 00:17:50.900
SHE HAS THE BABY
GRABBING ONTO HER
ALL THE TIME.

