WHAT DOES IT DO WHEN
I MOVE HER LEG?

00:17:55.730 --> 00:17:58.900
WHAT DOES IT DO WHEN
I MOVE THE OTHER LEG?

00:17:58.900 --> 00:18:01.800
Alda:
AND SOON I WAS PLAYING
MOTHER CHIMP.

00:18:01.800 --> 00:18:03.800
SO WHAT HAPPENS
IF I DO THIS?

