OH, YOU WANT TO DO PULL-UPS?

00:18:18.600 --> 00:18:21.130
OH, GOOD, VERY...
AND TWO AND THREE.

00:18:21.130 --> 00:18:23.900
ONE MORE, YOU CAN DO IT,
YOU CAN DO IT.

00:18:23.900 --> 00:18:25.060
AND FOUR.

00:18:25.060 --> 00:18:26.960
SHE'S SMILING, SHE LOVES IT.

00:18:26.960 --> 00:18:29.500
Alda:
IN THEIR OWN SOCIAL GROUPS

00:18:29.500 --> 00:18:33.560
YOUNG CHIMPS INTERACT WITH
RELATIVES OF ALL AGES--

00:18:33.560 --> 00:18:38.730
BROTHERS, SISTERS, COUSINS,
AUNTS AND UNCLES.

00:18:38.730 --> 00:18:41.130
THEY LEARN ESSENTIAL
CHIMP MANNERS

00:18:41.130 --> 00:18:44.730
THE DOs AND DON'Ts
OF CHIMP SOCIETY.

00:18:47.230 --> 00:18:51.560
MOST IMPORTANT, YOUNG FEMALES,
SOON TO BE MOTHERS THEMSELVES

00:18:51.560 --> 00:18:53.560
LEARN HOW TO HANDLE BABIES.

00:18:56.560 --> 00:19:00.130
SO IN THE NURSERY, YOUNG
FEMALE CHIMPS ARE ENCOURAGED

00:19:00.130 --> 00:19:02.100
TO PLAY WITH YOUNGER ANIMALS.

00:19:02.100 --> 00:19:03.800
TODAY, EVELYNE, AGE THREE

