WHEN THEY'RE NERVOUS

00:21:03.700 --> 00:21:05.730
BOTH TO MAKE YOU
A LITTLE CALMER

00:21:05.730 --> 00:21:07.960
AND TO MAKE HIM
CALMER IS TO GROOM.

00:21:07.960 --> 00:21:09.160
HOW WOULD
I DO THAT?

00:21:09.160 --> 00:21:10.700
DON'T LOOK AT THEIR FACE

00:21:10.700 --> 00:21:13.500
BUT YOU LOOK AT THE PART
THAT YOU'RE GROOMING

00:21:13.500 --> 00:21:15.760
AND IMMEDIATELY
YOU'RE GOING TO FIND

00:21:15.760 --> 00:21:17.400
THAT THEY RELAX
AND NOT MOVE

