SHE KNOWS THAT.

00:54:51.300 --> 00:54:54.330
AND SHE'S DOING THIS
LIP-SMACKING THING AT ME.

00:54:54.330 --> 00:54:56.530
THAT'S SIMPLY
A SIGN OF
ASSURANCE.

00:54:56.530 --> 00:54:59.060
IT'S NEITHER AGGRESSIVE
NOR SUBMISSIVE.

00:54:59.060 --> 00:55:00.930
SHE'S NOT BLOWING
ME KISSES?

